# ionpy - Python binding for ion-kit

```
pip3 install "git+https://github.com/fixstars/ion-kit.git#egg=ionpy&subdirectory=python"
```

## Test

```
LD_LIBRARY_PATH=<path-to-ion-libs> PYTHONPATH=. pytest ./tests/
```
